    <title>Authentication Endpoints</title>
    <para>You can use the Rackspace Cloud Identity authentication endpoints from version 1.1 or
        version 2.0. The legacy v1.1 API endpoint only provides authentication services, but you can
        use tokens from version 1.1 in version 2.0 API calls.</para>
    <important>
        <para>
            You can use either UK or US endpoints, regardless of where your account was created.
        </para>
    </important>
    <para> Rackspace recommends that you authenticate at one of the following Cloud Identity
        endpoints</para>
